title: True Power
overview: Sin City's blonde bombshell Hannah Harper stars as a sexy college girl with an insatiable desire for sex, sin and all the bling bling she can get.  So, our British tart takes a night job as a maid in an upscale brokerage house with plenty of deep dark secrets to hide...and a notorious reputation for seuxal shenanigans.  While at work, Elena (Hannah) uncovers more than she ever dreamed of...a company built on corruption and fueled by greed...sounds too good to be true!  So our girl uses her prime assets, and her dirty little mind to leverage herself into a serious position of "True Power"
